rows.label: qev065402_MSG0001
rows.name: Thank you! I'd honestly given up hope.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0002
rows.name: I can tell you, none of us went into this thing lightly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0003
rows.name:
But it didn't matterâ€”they knew we were coming.
Had a reception party all lined up and waiting.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0004
rows.name:
I don't get it. We were told they didn't know about the
intel Clemons got, and yet...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0005
rows.name:
I hate to even consider it, but that leak might have
been part of their plan from the beginning.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0006
rows.name:
Still, there's no way Clemons would fall for shady info
like that. Of all the BLADEs I know, not him...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0007
rows.name: Guess there's no point worrying about it here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0008
rows.name:
I'm afraid I'm the only one left now.
The mission's a total failure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0009
rows.name:
We need to extract out to New LA right now.
Planning our next move comes after.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0010
rows.name:
You go on ahead. I'm pretty shook up,
but I can make it back on my own.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0011
rows.name:
I'm banged and bruised, but I can walk okay.
I'll get back to the city in one piece.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065402_MSG0012
rows.name:
I need to give my report and make sure we don't lose
more lives like we did today.[ST:wait ]
